I know I wanted to become an aeronautical
engineer.

00:04:18.584 --> 00:04:20.454
What am I today?

00:04:20.454 --> 00:04:21.654
I'm an actor.

00:04:21.654 --> 00:04:22.744
I'm a singer.

00:04:22.744 --> 00:04:24.624
I'm an author.

00:04:24.624 --> 00:04:25.624
I'm a producer.

00:04:25.624 --> 00:04:26.624
I'm an artist.

00:04:26.624 --> 00:04:29.124
How did I go from becoming an engineer to
all of these things?

00:04:29.124 --> 00:04:33.104
I made choices, the choices that I wanted
for myself.

00:04:33.104 --> 00:04:39.104
So, that is my rule number two, let your dreams
fly.

00:04:39.104 --> 00:04:44.664
Give them wings, be who you want to be just
