00:04:48.824 --> 00:04:52.514
They are very funny thing, these opportunities,
they don't come very often.

00:04:52.514 --> 00:04:55.633
They come far and few in between.

00:04:55.633 --> 00:04:58.454
But when they do, do we recognize them?

00:04:58.454 --> 00:05:02.714
Our job is to recognize them and make the
most of them.

00:05:02.714 --> 00:05:07.174
I look back on all the things that I've done,
