00:05:32.504 --> 00:05:34.473
drop out of these opportunities.

00:05:34.473 --> 00:05:37.454
This, ladies and gentlemen is called drive.

00:05:37.454 --> 00:05:38.454
It's called ambition.

00:05:38.454 --> 00:05:44.813
So, no matter where you are in life, rule
