00:05:44.813 --> 00:05:49.163
to explore new opportunities.

00:05:49.163 --> 00:05:51.093
And there's nothing wrong with being ambitious.

00:05:51.093 --> 00:05:58.334
Ladies, listen to me.

00:05:58.334 --> 00:06:04.144
Now for all of you guys who like everything
in life, I don't think there's anything wrong

00:06:04.144 --> 00:06:09.044
with wanting to have the whole cake and eat
it too, nothing wrong.

00:06:09.044 --> 00:06:11.984
I want everything, I want everything.

00:06:11.984 --> 00:06:13.464
And there's nothing wrong with that.

00:06:13.464 --> 00:06:18.883
As long as you're not harming someone or doing
something wrong, don't be scared to want more

00:06:18.883 --> 00:06:21.734
for yourself than you ever thought you could.

00:06:21.734 --> 00:06:24.704
I'll give you a small example.

00:06:24.704 --> 00:06:31.314
A few years ago, I was shooting a film called
Don 2, you have heard of that, right?

00:06:31.314 --> 00:06:36.544
So, it was chosen to be shown at the Berlin
Film Festival, Berlinale and my entire team

00:06:36.544 --> 00:06:38.394
was flying for the premiere.

00:06:38.394 --> 00:06:39.654
And it was very exciting time.

00:06:39.654 --> 00:06:44.593
But at the same time, I was invited for the
first time to attend the Grammy Awards in

00:06:44.593 --> 00:06:45.794
LA.

00:06:45.794 --> 00:06:51.283
So, now when I was doing music, it was this
big choice, both the events were literally

00:06:51.283 --> 00:06:57.234
taking place one day apart in completely different
time zones, Berlin and LA.

00:06:57.234 --> 00:07:01.024
My team and everyone around me told me, no,
it can never happen.

00:07:01.024 --> 00:07:02.503
You have to choose what is your priority?

00:07:02.503 --> 00:07:09.873
And you know what I did, I made some insane
connections, Mumbai to London, London to Berlin,

00:07:09.873 --> 00:07:13.894
Berlin to Amsterdam, Amsterdam to LA, LA to
Mumbai in three days.

00:07:13.894 --> 00:07:19.374
And I made it happen.

00:07:19.374 --> 00:07:24.084
I went to both events and I looked great at
both events.

00:07:24.084 --> 00:07:28.973
Even though I hadn't slept, it took a little
bit of extra makeup, but I was fine.

00:07:28.973 --> 00:07:30.484
And that's not the only time I've done it.

00:07:30.484 --> 00:07:33.234
I've done it so many times over and over again.

00:07:33.234 --> 00:07:34.234
Why?

00:07:34.234 --> 00:07:38.084
Because I don't want anyone to tell me I can't
have everything.

00:07:38.084 --> 00:07:40.913
I want to dream of everything, and I'll have
everything.

00:07:40.913 --> 00:07:44.114
So, rule number four, be greedy.

00:07:44.114 --> 00:07:45.644
Be greedy for your ambitions.

00:07:45.644 --> 00:07:48.574
Be hungry for it.

00:07:48.574 --> 00:07:52.014
Don't live on someone else's benchmarks.

00:07:52.014 --> 00:07:57.723
We are told so many times in our life: ‘No
girl should do this, or you are elder boy

00:07:57.723 --> 00:08:02.473
in house, your responsibility is this, this
is who you should be.’

00:08:02.473 --> 00:08:05.454
Who can tell you who you should be?

00:08:05.454 --> 00:08:10.934
Don't let anyone or any situation dictate
to you who you are and who you can be.

00:08:10.934 --> 00:08:13.204
I know it's very much easier said than done.

00:08:13.204 --> 00:08:17.954
I know that because I've done it but fight
for your dreams because no one else is going

00:08:17.954 --> 00:08:20.944
to fight for your dreams, except you.

00:08:20.944 --> 00:08:25.663
I've turned down so many roles, opportunities
because they did not fit into what I thought

00:08:25.663 --> 00:08:28.424
at that time was the right thing for me.

00:08:28.424 --> 00:08:31.984
So, today my path is just my own.

00:08:31.984 --> 00:08:33.804
It belongs to no one.

00:08:33.804 --> 00:08:38.143
My failures, my successes, all of it, mine,
my journey, all of it is mine.

00:08:38.143 --> 00:08:42.754
So, rule number five, do not compromise.

00:08:42.754 --> 00:08:46.724
Do not settle on your dreams.

00:08:46.724 --> 00:08:48.114
Now who likes to fail?

